Commercial Manager (Indonesia)
Information:
Posted: 06 May 2014
Apply deadline: 04 Aug 2014
Location: Indonesia
Job description:
Commercial Manager                      IndonesiaDepartment : Support
DepartementKey Responsibilities will include:• Initially focus on
driving the implementation of a new ERP system• Implement streamlined
financial processes to improve efficiency and increase
profitability•Responsible for all financial and management aspects of the
Group•Provide leadership and coordination in the various business and
finance functions•Support Divisional Managers in making and implementing
strategic investment decisions•Responsible for statutory reporting in
Indonesia, Singapore  and other overseas locations•Ensuring compliance
with accounting standards and corporation law.Experience•Proven
experience in a senior positions in accounting, tax, finance and
management•At least 5 years in a private corporate environment including
Big Four tax division•Extensive staff management skills developed
through past experiences•Strategic role in defining and achieving
organisational goals and objectives•Strong technical expertise and
experience with ERP system integration and automationQualifications and
Personal Attributes•Degree qualification in Business, Accounting, Tax,
Finance and/or Systems•Post graduate studies in a relevant field is
advantageous•CA or CPA qualifications•Excellent English and Bahasa
language skills•Hands-on, accountable, pro-active, open and
independent•Build strong working relationships through teamwork, respect and
honesty at all levels
